# Prose + reference artifacts, not code (T2 decision, #267): the repo's markdown
# (CLAUDE.md, docs/, plan/) was never Prettier-formatted — a wholesale rewrite is
# hundreds of files of review noise for zero code-quality gain, and Prettier's md
# normalization (e.g. *em* -> _em_) rewrites carefully-authored prose. design/ is
# frozen design-mockup artifacts (html/jsx/css snapshots, not product code).
# .github/ belongs to the CI increment (T3, #267) and includes generated JSON
# (codeql-known-findings.json) that must stay byte-stable.
**/*.md
design/
.github/

